{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>After updating from <code class=\"language-text\">High Sierra</code> to <code class=\"language-text\">Mojave</code> in my macbook pro today, I found out that mojave have font render issue. But fix is simple.</p>\n<h3>Steps to Fix</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Copy the below code.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">defaults <span class=\"token function\">write</span> -g CGFontRenderingFontSmoothingDisabled -bool FALSE</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Open your terminal applicaiton.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Paste the copied code.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Restart your system.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>And this is how it looks before I fixed it.</p>\n<h3>Before fix</h3>\n<center>\n  \n  <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/Before-vscode-1d53dd2f6d2a16a70c3c4732e1ce7366-dfcc1.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n  \n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 62.643020594965684%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Before fix in VS Code\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/Before-vscode-1d53dd2f6d2a16a70c3c4732e1ce7366-fb8a0.png\" srcset=\"/static/Before-vscode-1d53dd2f6d2a16a70c3c4732e1ce7366-1a291.png 148w,\n/static/Before-vscode-1d53dd2f6d2a16a70c3c4732e1ce7366-2bc4a.png 295w,\n/static/Before-vscode-1d53dd2f6d2a16a70c3c4732e1ce7366-fb8a0.png 590w,\n/static/Before-vscode-1d53dd2f6d2a16a70c3c4732e1ce7366-526de.png 885w,\n/static/Before-vscode-1d53dd2f6d2a16a70c3c4732e1ce7366-fa2eb.png 1180w,\n/static/Before-vscode-1d53dd2f6d2a16a70c3c4732e1ce7366-08f6a.png 1770w,\n/static/Before-vscode-1d53dd2f6d2a16a70c3c4732e1ce7366-dfcc1.png 3496w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n</center>\n<h3>After fix</h3>\n<p>Restart the system to make it work.</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"October 21, 2018","path":"/blog/2018/fix-mojave-font-rendering-issue","title":"Fix Mojave Font Rendering Issue","readtime":null}}},"pageContext":{}}